e="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">Attending Physician or Hospital&nbsp; </span> <input name="Attending Physician's Name" size="132" type="text" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> &nbsp; </span><br /> <span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">Describe any Actions Taken or Treatment Given as a result of the incident:&nbsp; </span><br /> <textarea cols="70" name="Describe any treatment given: " rows="2"></textarea><br /> <span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">Name of Witness&nbsp; </span> <input name="Witness Name" size="18" type="text" /><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;"> Contact Person&nbsp; </span> <input name="Contact Person" size="20" type="text" /><br /> <span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">Date report submitted&nbsp; </span> <input name="Date Supervisor Submitted Report" size="5" type="text" /><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">Contact Phone # </span> <input name="Contact Phone Number" size="10" type="text" /><br /></span></span></span></span><hr /><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;"><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;"><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;"><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;"><span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS; font-size: x-small; color: #000080;">What could have been done to prevent the incident? (to be filled out by the supervisor):</span><br /> <span style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;"> <textarea cols="70" name="Corrective Actions" rows="2"></textarea></span><br /> </span></span></span></span><hr />
